897
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:43,520
I was seeing

898
00:40:43,520 --> 00:40:45,280
a different side of him

899
00:40:45,280 --> 00:40:47,680
I felt he was actually brave

900
00:40:48,240 --> 00:40:50,200
braver than I had imagined

901
00:40:52,680 --> 00:40:55,200
I was torn and hesitant

902
00:40:55,200 --> 00:40:56,240
I felt that I

903
00:40:56,240 --> 00:40:58,360
was too rigid about “feeling a spark”

904
00:40:58,880 --> 00:40:59,480
So

905
00:41:01,560 --> 00:41:02,960
it all felt really strange

906
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:04,040
I think people’s feelings

907
00:41:04,040 --> 00:41:05,520
and the way emotions arise

908
00:41:05,520 --> 00:41:06,720
often don’t really have

909
00:41:06,720 --> 00:41:08,720
a clear cause or reason

910
00:41:26,080 --> 00:41:28,360
I really agree with what he said

911
00:41:28,360 --> 00:41:30,040
Maybe we don’t have the time

912
00:41:30,040 --> 00:41:32,280
in just these ten‑plus days

913
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:34,560
to truly get to know each other

914
00:41:34,560 --> 00:41:35,760
Maybe after the house ends

915
00:41:35,760 --> 00:41:37,120
we might still have a bond

916
00:41:37,120 --> 00:41:38,000
or get another chance

917
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:41,000
to learn more about each other

918
00:41:42,200 --> 00:41:43,720
Life is so long

919
00:41:43,720 --> 00:41:46,880
no one can predict the future

920
00:42:24,480 --> 00:42:26,240
No

921
00:42:27,480 --> 00:42:29,520
I’ve already done what

922
00:42:29,520 --> 00:42:30,920
and said what

923
00:42:30,920 --> 00:42:32,760
I wanted to do and say

924
00:42:33,640 --> 00:42:36,120
I just wanted one last look at the house

925
00:42:39,600 --> 00:42:41,520
To look back at these days

926
00:42:41,520 --> 00:42:43,280
at the place we lived in

927
00:43:03,320 --> 00:43:04,120
I don’t really know why

928
00:43:04,120 --> 00:43:05,360
this whole thing, for me

929
00:43:05,360 --> 00:43:06,480
feels so heartbreaking

930
00:43:08,600 --> 00:43:09,640
It’s like

931
00:43:10,800 --> 00:43:12,600
a breakup kind of sadness

932
00:43:15,160 --> 00:43:19,080
like breaking up with my days here

933
00:43:53,160 --> 00:43:55,040
When I got the confession text

934
00:43:55,040 --> 00:43:56,200
my first thought was Yu An

935
00:43:56,840 --> 00:43:58,880
There was zero hesitation in that

936
00:44:04,760 --> 00:44:05,760
Are you cold?

937
00:44:05,760 --> 00:44:07,120
Yes

938
00:44:13,080 --> 00:44:14,080
You still remember this?

939
00:44:15,160 --> 00:44:15,960
The croissant?

940
00:44:15,960 --> 00:44:17,600
Yeah, on our first date

941
00:44:18,480 --> 00:44:19,840
I baked one for you

942
00:44:27,320 --> 00:44:27,960
Does it look similar?

943
00:44:29,120 --> 00:44:30,480
Even the color’s similar

944
00:44:30,480 --> 00:44:32,560
Yeah, that slightly burnt vibe

945
00:44:42,800 --> 00:44:44,400
Time really flies

946
00:44:44,400 --> 00:44:47,880
But I feel this brief ending

947
00:44:47,880 --> 00:44:49,080
is a better new beginning

948
00:44:52,880 --> 00:44:53,480
Without realizing it

949
00:44:53,480 --> 00:44:55,520
we’ve already gone through so many

950
00:44:57,040 --> 00:44:58,360
surprises and so much growth

951
00:44:59,560 --> 00:45:03,600
I think time and being together later

952
00:45:03,600 --> 00:45:05,560
will smooth out our sharp edges

953
00:45:05,560 --> 00:45:06,840
and heal our hearts

954
00:45:06,840 --> 00:45:07,120
Yeah

955
00:45:08,440 --> 00:45:10,360
I hope that

956
00:45:10,360 --> 00:45:11,600
one day in the future

957
00:45:11,600 --> 00:45:14,160
you can fully open yourself up

958
00:45:17,880 --> 00:45:18,440
I’m done

959
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:21,080
Okay, my turn. Hold this for me

960
00:45:22,680 --> 00:45:24,040
I’m afraid I’ll forget my lines

961
00:45:24,040 --> 00:45:25,320
so I wrote them down

962
00:45:27,480 --> 00:45:28,760
a little speech

963
00:45:34,720 --> 00:45:35,560
Teacher Yu,

964
00:45:36,280 --> 00:45:37,400
I never imagined

965
00:45:37,400 --> 00:45:39,400
I would meet someone here

966
00:45:39,400 --> 00:45:41,440
who seems so far from my type,

967
00:45:41,840 --> 00:45:44,240
someone I probably

968
00:45:44,240 --> 00:45:45,760
would not consider in real life.

969
00:45:46,960 --> 00:45:48,360
I am someone

970
00:45:48,800 --> 00:45:51,280
with a very high bar for liking someone.

971
00:45:51,960 --> 00:45:53,880
I do not easily say

972
00:45:53,880 --> 00:45:55,200
the words “I like you.”

973
00:45:56,800 --> 00:45:58,240
But when I realized

974
00:45:58,240 --> 00:46:00,960
I think of you without noticing,

975
00:46:01,720 --> 00:46:04,040
and smile every time you cross my mind,

976
00:46:05,400 --> 00:46:07,320
and even feel shy looking at you,

977
00:46:08,840 --> 00:46:10,920
and my mood is swayed by you,

978
00:46:12,680 --> 00:46:13,880
that was when I realized

979
00:46:16,360 --> 00:46:17,120
I like you.

980
00:46:21,920 --> 00:46:23,960
Although we are very different,

981
00:46:24,720 --> 00:46:26,320
each with our own rough edges,

982
00:46:26,840 --> 00:46:28,200
and we still need time

983
00:46:28,200 --> 00:46:31,080
to be together and to adjust,

984
00:46:31,600 --> 00:46:33,560
you made me believe

985
00:46:33,560 --> 00:46:35,680
you are willing to spend time

986
00:46:35,680 --> 00:46:37,440
facing everything together with me.

987
00:46:38,080 --> 00:46:39,960
You are willing to stay by my side,

988
00:46:39,960 --> 00:46:41,360
to walk this path with me.

989
00:46:41,920 --> 00:46:44,040
You are willing to wait for me

990
00:46:44,640 --> 00:46:47,680
as I slowly peel off

991
00:46:47,680 --> 00:46:49,480
my hard protective shell again.

992
00:46:50,800 --> 00:46:52,160
You once said

993
00:46:52,160 --> 00:46:54,640
you used to be someone who

994
00:46:54,640 --> 00:46:55,960
had little patience for love

995
00:46:55,960 --> 00:46:57,560
and was quite self-centered.

996
00:46:58,080 --> 00:46:59,240
And I am also someone

997
00:46:59,240 --> 00:47:01,440
who, being too rational,

998
00:47:01,760 --> 00:47:03,840
gives up from thinking too much.

999
00:47:04,760 --> 00:47:07,920
Leaving the house today is just our start.

1000
00:47:09,000 --> 00:47:11,920
I am willing to spend time to try again.

1001
00:47:12,760 --> 00:47:16,120
Shall we take another leap together?

1002
00:47:16,120 --> 00:47:18,240
One more leap together, okay?

1003
00:47:18,240 --> 00:47:19,360
No problem, let us go for it.

1004
00:47:27,560 --> 00:47:28,280
Let us go.

1005
00:47:41,840 --> 00:47:43,400
She finally said the words “I like you.”

1006
00:47:44,960 --> 00:47:45,880
It really feels like

1007
00:47:46,600 --> 00:47:48,440
my heart is thumping like a fawn.

1008
00:47:50,920 --> 00:47:51,640
You did not cry, right?

1009
00:47:51,840 --> 00:47:53,080
I brought you tissues.

1010
00:47:53,280 --> 00:47:54,040
No.

1011
00:47:54,520 --> 00:47:55,720
It is just the wind is strong.

1012
00:48:00,600 --> 00:48:02,640
Those fluttery feelings

1013
00:48:02,640 --> 00:48:04,520
I have for him,

1014
00:48:04,520 --> 00:48:05,560
I admit them.

1015
00:48:05,560 --> 00:48:07,520
They are the feelings of liking him.

1016
00:48:07,520 --> 00:48:09,320
So this time I really hope

1017
00:48:09,320 --> 00:48:12,680
I can give us both a chance,

1018
00:48:12,680 --> 00:48:15,040
to try once more together.

1019
00:48:16,400 --> 00:48:17,520
Want to jump around a bit?

1020
00:48:17,520 --> 00:48:19,480
Jump around? Are you crazy?

1021
00:48:24,800 --> 00:48:27,560
My “leap” means keep on trying.

1022
00:48:28,040 --> 00:48:29,640
You still need to keep it up.

1023
00:48:30,440 --> 00:48:32,360
You cannot just give up.

1024
00:48:33,040 --> 00:48:34,240
I already gave up ages ago.

1025
00:48:34,240 --> 00:48:35,000
Excuse me,

1026
00:48:42,440 --> 00:48:43,640
someone is back.

1027
00:48:45,160 --> 00:48:46,680
The two of them came back together.

1028
00:48:50,600 --> 00:48:51,640
So jealous.

1029
00:48:54,000 --> 00:48:55,520
Sis, hurry up.

1030
00:48:55,520 --> 00:48:57,240
I want to squeeze you two together.

1031
00:48:59,440 --> 00:48:59,920
Is there this kind of

1032
00:48:59,920 --> 00:49:02,480
feeling of being this excited?

1033
00:49:02,480 --> 00:49:03,480
Come on, everyone.

1034
00:49:03,480 --> 00:49:04,560
How could I not be excited?

1035
00:49:07,520 --> 00:49:08,320
Lao Sun is out.

1036
00:49:08,720 --> 00:49:09,560
Really?

1037
00:49:11,520 --> 00:49:12,400
Here she comes.

1038
00:49:19,360 --> 00:49:20,160
Look at her outfit,

1039
00:49:20,160 --> 00:49:21,680
does it look like a wedding dress?

1040
00:49:23,480 --> 00:49:26,080
Lao Sun!
